Framework:
- definition of pain
- pain as a protective signal and not our enemy
- opioids and chronic pain crisis
- strategic approaches to pain 
- addressing pain with a 6 pillar health approach
- listening closely to our bodies and their signals
- accepting responsibility for our health 
- empowerment to address the pain we experience



